9858	2026-01-27 22:59:04	MSFT	Investing.com	Zijin Mining shares hit record high on plan to buy Canada’s Allied Gold\n\nZijin Mining Group's shares reached a record high after announcing a plan to acquire Canada-listed Allied Gold Corp for approximately C$5.5 billion ($4.0 billion). This acquisition will expand Zijin's global gold portfolio, adding operational mines in Mali and Côte d'Ivoire, and a project in Ethiopia expected to begin production in late 2026. The deal is set to increase Zijin's gold reserves and future output at a time of near-record gold prices, with Allied Gold's annual production projected to reach 25 tonnes by 2029.	0.52	NEWS	\N	\N	https://www.investing.com/news/stock-market-news/zijin-mining-shares-hit-record-high-on-plan-to-buy-canadas-allied-gold-4466338	\N	[0.0033738925,-0.01413461,0.022445127,0.008429203,0.05748038,-0.031156868,0.0031035568,-0.033493243,-0.03465522,0.014438694,-0.07589006,0.036834817,-0.06502603,0.05697246,-0.037013296,0.023984184,0.015780428,-0.0019250462,0.009226831,0.034121696,0.0144415535,0.0056362236,-0.012661727,0.029815719,0.021706428,-0.004601067,0.00655889,-0.06413358,-0.0129809575,-0.022959607,-0.020374995,-0.060969077,-0.03764376,0.033814996,2.3526711e-06,-0.06777044,-0.022725822,0.03213668,0.05508199,0.062270656,-0.06991185,-0.009989522,-0.060488377,0.052203473,-0.021058774,-0.081782885,-0.036002714,-0.015055696,-0.01744927,0.02579845,0.007058876,0.015507289,0.021227738,-0.017857105,-0.07873932,-0.15086026,0.043272033,-0.010214944,-0.0029677209,0.018221775,0.030517008,0.046007976,-0.003389101,-0.07535776,0.025898302,0.017847763,0.090138346,0.033776738,0.039065544,-0.004635903,0.012687508,0.044997685,0.008946505,-0.0013578038,0.012305127,-0.019631123,-6.169715e-05,0.08415528,0.007180131,-0.0064876103,-0.018121172,0.040432636,0.007539905,0.0032314218,-0.03571147,0.02533166,-0.052669972,-0.012622714,0.020085832,-0.017922238,-0.016795732,-0.019207144,-0.0057231425,0.044868086,-0.0394598,0.038602844,0.01908317,-0.009